reviewText: My sister and I grew up with these videos and I was glad I found this one. This is a great show for anyone who loves the little mermaid.
This was a great video and brought back some wonderful childhood memories!!
I had this movie and lost it - my grandaughter loves it so i was really pleased to be able to replace it - great service - thanks
